sed with him, said, \u201cFasting is not merely from food and drink alone. Rather, it is from lies, falsehood, vain talk, and swearing.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 8882 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064f \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0633\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0651\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064f \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0651\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14887,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/10\/must-eat-suhoor\/","url_meta":{"origin":24887,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Suhur: Eat the blessed pre-fasting meal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Miqdam ibn Ma\u2019dikarib reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYou must take the pre-fasting meal, for it is a blessed meal.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 2164 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0642\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0639\u0652\u062f\u0650\u064a\u0643\u064e\u0631\u0650\u0628\u064e\u00a0\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0643\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0628\u0650\u063a\u064e\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0651\u064f\u062d\u064f\u0648\u0631\u0650 \u0641\u064e\u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0647\u064f\u0648\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4541,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/09\/fasting-shield-battle\/","url_meta":{"origin":24887,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Siyam: Fasting is like a shield in battle","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 9, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Uthman ibn Abi al-'As reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFasting is a shield from the Hellfire, just like a shield of yours in battle.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 1639 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u062b\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0635\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3761,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/23\/prophet-observed-wasala-fasting\/","url_meta":{"origin":24887,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: The Prophet continuously fasted, Muslims may not","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 23, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would observe continuous fasting during the month of Ramadan and so did the people, but he prohibited them. It was said, \u201cYou are continuously fasting.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cVerily, I am not like you, for I am\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14890,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/10\/do-not-neglect-suhur\/","url_meta":{"origin":24887,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Suhoor: Do not neglect blessed pre-fasting meal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn al-Harith reported: A man among the companions entered upon the Prophet while he was eating the pre-fasting meal. The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, it is a blessing that Allah has given you, so do not abandon it.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 2162 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23295,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/06\/23\/siyam-sawm-lies-obscenity-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":24887,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Siyam: True fasting is from falsehood and sin","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 23, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, fasting is not only from eating and drinking. Rather, fasting is from vanity and obscenity. If someone abuses you or acts foolish against you, then say: Indeed, I am fasting.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 3479\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/24887","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=24887"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/24887\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=24887"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=24887"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=24887"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}